  "subject": "[SDC] Fix sdc schema init race condition",
  "commit_message": "[SDC] Fix sdc schema init race condition\n\n- wait on the sdc-cs job before starting sdc-be\n- this fixes transient gating issues that happen when\n  tests start using sdc-be while the sdc db schema is still\n  being initialized by sdc-cs\n\nIssue-ID: OOM-3388\nChange-Id: I6e06ffaeb0daa4093fdee141cd8bc86d797214a2\nSigned-off-by: Fiete Ostkamp <fiete.ostkamp@telekom.de>\n",
